+- The existing `cypherclaw.narrative_api` pattern is a FastAPI `create_app(...)` factory with injected test doubles, lazy deploy-side imports, narrow request schemas, auth dependencies on protected endpoints, and helper modules that normalize flexible engine return shapes.
