+- The StoryBeat shape is owned by the narrative engine. Deniable's bridge requires `id`, `cycle_number`, and `arc_position` while preserving the full raw payload, so this endpoint should serialize the in-process beat without adding null/default fields from an over-constrained response schema.
+- The generated hardening bullets about SenseWeave self-critique/resource-governor wiring and daemon identity startup are outside this endpoint's affected area. Startup identity remains covered by `tests/test_narrative_api_main.py`, `tests/test_first_boot.py`, and `tests/test_governor_integration.py`; no new dependencies or migrations are required for T-011.
+
+## T-011@20260502T001347Z Verification
+
+- Red phase confirmed before implementation: `pytest tests/test_narrative_api_beats.py -q` failed with `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'cypherclaw.narrative_api.beats'`.
+- Endpoint and existing narrative API tests passed: `pytest tests/test_narrative_api_beats.py tests/test_narrative_api_memory.py tests/test_narrative_api_events.py tests/test_narrative_api_health.py tests/test_narrative_api_main.py -q` reported `47 passed`.
+- Candidate hardening anchors passed: `pytest tests/test_self_critique.py::TestPipelineIntegration tests/test_resource_governor.py tests/test_governor_integration.py::TestStartupIdentityWiring -q` reported `32 passed`.
+- Required validation passed: `pip install -e '.[dev]' && pytest tests/ -x && ruff check src/ tests/ && mypy src/` reported `3866 passed, 3 skipped`; ruff and mypy were clean.
